text: The Robert B. and Estelle J. Webb House is located in Florence, Wisconsin. ==History== Robert was involved in mining and ran a hardware store in Florence. The house was added to the State Register of Historic Places in 2013 and to the National Register of Historic Places the following year. ==References== Category:Houses on the National Register of Historic Places in Wisconsin Category:National Register of Historic Places in Florence County, Wisconsin Category:Queen Anne architecture in Wisconsin Category:Houses completed in 1883
title: Robert B. and Estelle J. Webb House
